@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@organizationId = 1

### Block an organization (NOT_ACCREDITED -> BLOCKED)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/organizations/{{organizationId}}/blocked HTTP/1.1

### Unblock an organization (BLOCKED -> NOT_ACCREDITED or ACCREDITED)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/organizations/{{organizationId}}/blocked HTTP/1.1

### Toggle blocked - Non-existent organization (should return 404)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/organizations/999999/blocked HTTP/1.1
